When galleries are open (close until August 2017) there are gender neutral bathrooms on the first and second floor, but admission is required to get to these.

name: Tower Theaters
directions: Park in back and enter Tower Theaters by the Underlings lingerie. Take elevator to floor 2 or go up spiral staircase and there's a public bathroom by movie theater entrance. They claim to lock the building after the last movie gets out but I've been in my office since 2-3 am and never noticed them actually lock it. Great movie theater too. Very small, friendly, accessible.
